
## React Router v7

This project includes [React Router v7](https://reactrouter.com) for client-side routing.

### Quick Start

Add new routes in `src/routes/AppRoutes.tsx`:

```tsx
import About from '@/pages/About';
// ...
<Route path="/about" element={<About />} />
```

Navigate using `<Link>`:

```tsx
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
// ...
<Link to="/about">About</Link>
```

### Learn More

- [React Router v7 Documentation](https://reactrouter.com)
